M\left[\hat{p}\left(x\right)\right]=\frac{1}{nh}\sum_{i=1}^{n}\intop_{-\infty}^{+\infty}K\left(\frac{x_{i}-x}{h}\right)p\left(x_{i}\right)dx_{i}.
